The Meso-NH model is a non-hydrostatic atmospheric model. It has been jointly
developed by the Laboratoire d'Aérologie (UMR 5560 UPS/CNRS) and by CNRM-GAME
(UMR 3589 CNRS/Météo-France). The holders of Meso-NH software are
Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique CNRS, Météo-France and
Université Paul Sabatier.

